OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly, but bright start.
OL,6,FPlenty of sunny spells through the
OL,7,Fday, though cloudier skies at times in
OL,8,Fthe west. A few splashes of rain
OL,9,Fpossible for Northern Ireland and
OL,10,Fnorthwest Scotland. Breezy in the
OL,11,Fwest. Feeling warmer for many.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine evening, though
OL,14,Fturning chilly again under the clear
OL,15,Fspells overnight, with a patchy frost
OL,16,Fin the east. A few showers still
OL,17,Fpossible in the far northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
