OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FMost places dry with sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Cloud and outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fmoving across Northern Ireland and
OL,8,Fwestern Scotland during the afternoon.
OL,9,FBreezy in the west. Feeling warm in
OL,10,Fthe sunshine.
